message:
fix: address 7 bugs from codebase review

1. providers/anthropic_stream.go — check scanner.Err() after SSE loop;
   truncated responses returned silently on network errors

2. config/config_load.go — trim whitespace in GOCLAW_OWNER_IDS;
   trailing spaces caused owner exact-match failures

3. cron/service.go — handle saveUnsafe() errors at 5 call sites;
   disk I/O failures lost cron state silently

4. tasks/task_ticker.go — separate timeouts for followups (15s) and
   recovery (30s); shared con
